      "text": "Nolan was a beloved son, student-athlete, &amp; a Black boy who deserved to grow old.\n\nThough true justice would mean Nolan would be alive today, we’re pushing for the accountability his family deserves.\n\nI grieve for his loved ones &amp; join their demands for an independent",
