      "text": "My heart is with the family &amp; loved ones of Louisa Gag, a beloved community member &amp; public servant committed to making Boston a safer &amp; more accessible city.\n\nHer dedication to improving the livability of our streets, neighborhoods, &amp; public spaces has made Boston a better",
